TopicTitle: No Text on Alt-F12 menu or when i click on a kerbal (IVA OVA bubbles but no text)

Articles.Content:
Very strange issue i am running Win 7 64 Bit and i am having an issue with text not displaying only in certain menus. There is no problem with most text in the game all settings menus show text the only two areas that i have noticed this issue is when i push ALT-F12 all the bubble are there and select-able but there is no text in any of them what so ever, Also during flight if i hover over a kerbal i get the two bubbles for internal view and space walk options (dont remember the abbreviations) they also do not show text at all my game is un modded and has been fresh installed 3 times with nothing fixing it.

I am runing a

R9 270x

fx 6300 hex core 3.4 Ghz

8 Gb of 2300 ram

previous versions of KSP have worked flawlessly
Can you post an output_log.txt file, please?
